Comics_text_box: I DON'T THINK YOU'VE CAPTURED THE SPIRIT OF THIS RESOLUTION THING.
column3: YOU'RE JUST JEALOUS BECAUSE I TOOK ALL THE GOOD ONES.

Comics_text_box: I RESOLVE TO SHOW NO TOLERANCE FOR THOSE LESS FORTUNATE...
column3: REDEFINE MORALITY TO  SUIT MY SHORT TERM OBJECTIVES...
column4: AND CONQUER THE PLANET EARTH AND MAKE ALL THE INHABITANTS MY SLAVES.

Comics_text_box: DO YOU HAVE ANY NEW YEAR'S RESOLUTIONS?
